### EduPortal API - Career Assessments Controller
### Career assessment management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/career-assessments
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL CAREER ASSESSMENTS
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET CAREER ASSESSMENT SUMMARIES
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/summaries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET CAREER ASSESSMENT BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET CAREER ASSESSMENTS BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET CAREER ASSESSMENTS BY COACH
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/coach/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET CAREER ASSESSMENT STATISTICS
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE CAREER ASSESSMENT - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "coachId": 1,
  "assessmentDate": "2024-11-15",
  "careerInterests": ["Engineering", "Technology"],
  "strengths": ["Problem Solving", "Analytical Thinking"],
  "areasForImprovement": ["Communication"],
  "recommendedPaths": ["Computer Science", "Data Science"],
  "notes": "Kariyer değerlendirmesi"
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE CAREER ASSESSMENT - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "careerInterests": ["Engineering", "Research"],
  "recommendedPaths": ["AI Research", "Machine Learning"],
  "notes": "Güncellenmiş değerlendirme"
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE CAREER ASSESSMENT - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

